Title: Minimal shim of lares for Robyn (fit path only)
Version: 5.3.0
Authors@R: person("Shim","Shim", role=c("aut","cre"), email="shim@example.com")
Description: Provides only the lares functions Robyn imports, so Robyn installs and runs its
